ame%22,%22monetizedUrl%22:%22https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?toolid=10001&amp;mkcid=1&amp;campid=5338497749&amp;mkevt=1&amp;_trkparms=5079:5000006401&amp;mkrid=711-53200-19255-0&amp;customid=%5Bsubid_value%5D%22,%22rawUrl%22:%22https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?_trkparms=5079:5000006401%22%7D\" class=\"norewrite\">           <a class=\"js-lead-click-event-tracking  monetized-link\" href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?toolid=10001&amp;mkcid=1&amp;campid=5338497749&amp;mkevt=1&amp;_trkparms=5079:5000006401&amp;mkrid=711-53200-19255-0&amp;customid=subid_value\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/www.ebay.com\\/itm\\/125514868264?_trkparms=5079:5000006401&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?_trkparms=5079:5000006401\">get the controller for $110 and receive a free game</a> </span> with your purchase. Both of those are awesome deals. Antonline is selling the Elite Series 2 Core controller bundled with Watch Dogs: Legion via its eBay account. Since Antonline is a Microsoft authorized seller, you can rest assured that this deal is legit.</p><div title=\"\" data-embed-type=\"buylink\" data-ref-id=\"undefined\" data-template=\"undefined\" data-size=\"buylink__small\" data-title=\"\" data-collection=\"%7B%22text%22:%22See%20deal%20at%20Newegg%22,%22monetizedUrl%22:%22https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=VZfI20jEa0c&amp;mid=44583&amp;u1=subid_value&amp;murl=https://www.newegg.com/p/N82E16874103724%22,%22rawUrl%22:%22https://www.newegg.com/p/N82E16874103724%22%7D\" class=\"norewrite\">           <a class=\"js-lead-click-event-tracking  monetized-link\" href=\"https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=VZfI20jEa0c&amp;mid=44583&amp;u1=subid_value&amp;murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newegg.com%2Fp%2FN82E16874103724\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/www.newegg.com\\/p\\/N82E16874103724&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;buylink|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;buylink|button&quot;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.newegg.com/p/N82E16874103724\">See deal at Newegg</a> </div><div title=\"\" data-embed-type=\"buylink\" data-ref-id=\"undefined\" data-template=\"undefined\" data-size=\"buylink__small\" data-title=\"\" data-collection=\"%7B%22text%22:%22See%20deal%20at%20eBay%22,%22monetizedUrl%22:%22https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?toolid=10001&amp;mkcid=1&amp;campid=5338497749&amp;mkevt=1&amp;_trkparms=5079:5000006401&amp;mkrid=711-53200-19255-0&amp;customid=%5Bsubid_value%5D%22,%22rawUrl%22:%22https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?_trkparms=5079:5000006401%22%7D\" class=\"norewrite\">           <a class=\"js-lead-click-event-tracking  monetized-link\" href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?toolid=10001&amp;mkcid=1&amp;campid=5338497749&amp;mkevt=1&amp;_trkparms=5079:5000006401&amp;mkrid=711-53200-19255-0&amp;customid=subid_value\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/www.ebay.com\\/itm\\/125514868264?_trkparms=5079:5000006401&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;buylink|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;buylink|button&quot;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/125514868264?_trkparms=5079:5000006401\">See deal at eBay</a> </div><p>The code for Watch Dogs: Legion will arrive in your inbox within 10 days of purchase. Legion is the latest entry in the open-world hacker franchise, and it includes a pretty clever gameplay feature that allows you to control any NPC in the game. Legion offers a nice variety of missions, plenty of cool gadgets, and a large open-world sandbox to explore. We awarded the game an 8/10 in our <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/watch-dogs-legion-review/1900-6417594/\" data-ref-id=\"1900-6417594\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/watch-dogs-legion-review/1900-6417594/\">Watch Dogs: Legion review</a>.</p><p>As mentioned already, the Elite Series 2 Core controller doesn't come with any attachments. That means you won't get back paddles, four extra analog sticks to swap, a swappable D-pad, or the carrying case. Instead, the Core controller simply features the premium build of the Elite Series 2 controller--nicer sticks, trigger locks, an eight-way metal D-pad, and tactile handle grips.</p><p>If you decide you want the back paddles and other accessories, you can always purchase them separately. Microsoft is selling the <span data-embed-type=\"buylink\" data-size=\"buylink__embed\" data-collection=\"%7B%22text%22:%22Complete%20Component%20Pack%20for%20$60.%22,%22monetizedUrl%22:%22https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=VZfI20jEa0c&amp;mid=24542&amp;u1=%5Bsubid_value%5D&amp;murl=https://www.xbox.com/en-US/accessories/controllers/complete-component-pack%22,%22rawUrl%22:%22https://www.xbox.com/en-US/accessories/controllers/complete-component-pack%22%7D\" class=\"norewrite\">           <a class=\"js-lead-click-event-tracking  monetized-link\" href=\"https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=VZfI20jEa0c&amp;mid=24542&amp;u1=[subid_value]&amp;murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-US%2Faccessories%2Fcontrollers%2Fcomplete-component-pack\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/www.xbox.com\\/en-US\\/accessories\\/controllers\\/complete-component-pack&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.xbox.com/en-US/accessories/controllers/complete-component-pack\">Complete Component Pack for $60.</a> </span> Alternatively, you can pick and choose which swappable parts you want and buy them from third-party companies. For instance, you can get a <span data-embed-type=\"buylink\" data-size=\"buylink__embed\" data-collection=\"%7B%22text%22:%22nice%20set%20of%20back%20paddles%20for%20around%20$10.%22,%22monetizedUrl%22:%22https://www.amazon.com/eXtremeRate-Stainless-Replacement-Accessories-Controller/dp/B01LSQNWZY?tag=gs-buybutton-20%22,%22rawUrl%22:%22https://www.amazon.com/eXtremeRate-Stainless-Replacement-Accessories-Controller/dp/B01LSQNWZY%22%7D\" class=\"norewrite\">           <a class=\"js-lead-click-event-tracking  monetized-link\" href=\"https://assoc-redirect.amazon.com/g/r/https://www.amazon.com/eXtremeRate-Stainless-Replacement-Accessories-Controller/dp/B01LSQNWZY?tag=gamespotdeals-20&amp;ascsubtag=ag%3Ags-1100-6507777%7Cvg%3Aeb23ff37-a8b2-4860-aa83-7be89b0bbae4%7Cst%3Adtp\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/assoc-redirect.amazon.com\\/g\\/r\\/https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/eXtremeRate-Stainless-Replacement-Accessories-Controller\\/dp\\/B01LSQNWZY?tag=gamespotdeals-20&amp;ascsubtag=ag%3Ags-1100-6507777%7Cvg%3A-%7Cst%3Adtp&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://assoc-redirect.amazon.com/g/r/https://www.amazon.com/eXtremeRate-Stainless-Replacement-Accessories-Controller/dp/B01LSQNWZY?tag=gamespotdeals-20&amp;ascsubtag=ag%3Ags-1100-6507777%7Cvg%3A-%7Cst%3Adtp\">nice set of back paddles for around $10.</a> </span> We've tested these third-party paddles and they feel good and work well.</p><p>If you're interested in Watch Dogs: Legion but aren't sold on the Elite Series 2 controller, you can also currently <span data-embed-type=\"buylink\" data-size=\"buylink__embed\" data-collection=\"%7B%22text%22:%22get%20the%20game%20bundled%20with%20the%20standard%20Xbox%20wireless%20controller%20for%20$50.%22,%22monetizedUrl%22:%22https://www.ebay.com/itm/295221413697?toolid=10001&amp;mkcid=1&amp;campid=5338497749&amp;mkevt=1&amp;mkrid=711-53200-19255-0&amp;customid=%5Bsubid_value%5D%22,%22rawUrl%22:%22https://www.ebay.com/itm/295221413697%22%7D\" class=\"norewrite\">           <a class=\"js-lead-click-event-tracking  monetized-link\" href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/295221413697?toolid=10001&amp;mkcid=1&amp;campid=5338497749&amp;mkevt=1&amp;mkrid=711-53200-19255-0&amp;customid=subid_value\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/www.ebay.com\\/itm\\/295221413697&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;buylink|embedded-link&quot;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/295221413697\">get the game bundled with the standard Xbox wireless controller for $50.</a> </span></p><p><em>Editor's Note: Article updated on November 15, 2022</em></p><div data-embed-type=\"imageGallery\" data-ref-id=\"4252\"><div class=\"image-gallery__header\">The 24 Biggest Upcoming Xbox Exclusives</div><div class=\"image-gallery__main\"><div class=\"image-gallery__item\"><img src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/screen_medium/1702/17023653/4018098-everwild.jpg\"></div><div class=\"image-gallery__item\"><img src=\"https://www.games